cu.explanation_en: Setting the F1AP log level to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors and may prevent proper F1AP protocol handling.

du.explanation_en: Setting the F1AP log level to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors and may prevent proper F1AP protocol handling.
du.explanation_zh: 將 F1AP 日誌等級設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid'，會導致日誌配置錯誤，並可能阻止正確的 F1AP 協議處理。
